#### Authorizations

HTTPBasicHTTPBearerHTTPBasicHTTPBearer

​

Authorization

string

header

required

Basic authentication header of the form `Basic <encoded-value>`, where `<encoded-value>` is the base64-encoded string `username:password`.

#### Body

application/json

Request to get the structured chat / trajectory view for a trace.

​

project_id

string

required

​

trace_id

string

required

​

include_feedback

boolean

default:false

#### Response

Successful Response

Structured chat view: a linear sequence of messages representing the agent trajectory for a single trace.

​

trace_id

string

required

​

root_span_name

string | null

​

provider

string | null

​

total_duration_ms

integer | null

Wall-clock duration of the trace root span in milliseconds. This is not a sum of child span durations.

